title: Fan And Case, 1810–20
creditline: Gift of Georgina and Louisa L. Schuyler
description: Fan case has removable lid. Reversible "four-way" brisé fan. Sticks of drilled and painted bone; silk connecting ribbon; mother-of-pearl washer at the rivet.

tombstone.epitaph:
Fan And Case, 1810–20.
1810–20. H x W (open): 16.2 x 29.8 cm (6 3/8 x 11 3/4 in.). Gift of Georgina and Louisa L. Schuyler. 1916-29-122-a,b.
